<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:08:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>极端正统的犹太人不会在一夜之间被强行加入以色列国防军，但变化即将到来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-jews-wont-be-press-ganged-into-the-idf-overnight-but-change-is-coming/0000018e-99fe-dcec-a3ef-dbffd16e0000</link><description>犹太学院学生的兵役自动豁免期满之际，极端正统派社区正在发生重大变化。那些处于边缘的人逐渐意识到，必须真正融入以色列社会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-jews-wont-be-press-ganged-into-the-idf-overnight-but-change-is-coming/0000018e-99fe-dcec-a3ef-dbffd16e0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其反对派对独裁者埃尔多安造成令人震惊的打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/turkeys-opposition-lands-authoritarian-erdogan-a-shocking-blow/0000018e-9a35-dd2b-ad9f-da7f48730000</link><description>周日晚上，土耳其书写了历史：反对派在地方选举中取得如此巨大的胜利，标志着埃尔多安下台的第一天，以及重建正常运转的民主的机会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/turkeys-opposition-lands-authoritarian-erdogan-a-shocking-blow/0000018e-9a35-dd2b-ad9f-da7f48730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列依靠武力，自取自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-israel-relies-on-force-it-sets-itself-up-for-suicide/0000018e-99e1-dd2b-ad9f-d9fb98760000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:43:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-israel-relies-on-force-it-sets-itself-up-for-suicide/0000018e-99e1-dd2b-ad9f-d9fb98760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会通过内塔尼亚胡支持的法律，允许因加沙战争报道而“立即”关闭以色列半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/netanyahu-pushes-ahead-law-for-immediate-shutdown-of-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018e-99f0-de2c-afff-bbf8be670000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的联盟于11月搁置了该法律的早期版本，因为担心它可能会破坏卡塔尔在以色列和哈马斯之间人质谈判中的调解努力</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/netanyahu-pushes-ahead-law-for-immediate-shutdown-of-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018e-99f0-de2c-afff-bbf8be670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方表示，对加沙的希法医院进行突袭可能会获得有关以色列人质的重要情报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-al-shifa-hospital-raid-may-yield-crucial-intel-about-hostages/0000018e-99a8-de2c-afff-bbe8d5ab0000</link><description>参加此次行动的以色列国防军高级军官表示，以色列军队发现了 10 月 7 日发生的事件的文件，可以提供有关加沙哈马斯扣押的以色列人质的信息</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 13:26:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-al-shifa-hospital-raid-may-yield-crucial-intel-about-hostages/0000018e-99a8-de2c-afff-bbe8d5ab0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的巴勒斯坦人像我一样不断游行以保护我们的土地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-palestinians-in-israel-like-me-keep-marching-to-protect-our-land/0000018e-996f-de2c-afff-bbef3b1f0000</link><description>土地日纪念 1976 年被以色列军队杀害的六名反对征用土地的手无寸铁的抗议者。我们绿线两侧的巴勒斯坦人仍然生活在它的遗产中。今年，一些人梦想着以色列重新占领加沙，这比以往任何时候都更加重要</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 13:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-palestinians-in-israel-like-me-keep-marching-to-protect-our-land/0000018e-996f-de2c-afff-bbef3b1f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人重新开始预订出国旅行。只是不要称之为假期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-are-back-to-booking-trips-abroad-just-dont-call-it-a-vacation/0000018e-98d7-d45a-a5be-b8d764ea0000</link><description>尽管战争仍在继续，机票价格也很高，但以色列人仍在计划逾越节及以后的航班。他们选择提供安全感的目的地，其中包括亚洲、美国和岛屿</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-are-back-to-booking-trips-abroad-just-dont-call-it-a-vacation/0000018e-98d7-d45a-a5be-b8d764ea0000</guid></item><item><title>“冲击议会！”耶路撒冷的大规模反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动要求采取更激进的措施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/storm-the-knesset-large-anti-netanyahu-protest-leaves-some-demanding-more-radical-steps/0000018e-9991-dd2b-ad9f-d9dbbf440000</link><description>数百个帐篷在耶路撒冷搭建起来，进行为期四天的抗议活动，示威者对政府即将进入春季休会感到愤怒，呼吁举行新的选举。但对于一些人来说，这是一个错失的机会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:36:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/storm-the-knesset-large-anti-netanyahu-protest-leaves-some-demanding-more-radical-steps/0000018e-9991-dd2b-ad9f-d9dbbf440000</guid></item><item><title>“我们无声”：记者向阿拉伯世界介绍以色列境内的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-are-voiceless-the-journalist-educating-the-arab-world-about-palestinians-in-israel/0000018e-94fe-d4de-afee-f4ff167b0000</link><description>出生于拿撒勒的穆斯塔法·卡布拉维 (Mustafa Qablawi) 最近搬到了约旦河西岸，从那里他开始接触世界各地的巴勒斯坦人，希望他们能够了解以色列的巴勒斯坦人面临的挑战，特别是自 10 月 7 日以来的挑战。“以色列的巴勒斯坦人是孤儿”。他告诉国土报</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-are-voiceless-the-journalist-educating-the-arab-world-about-palestinians-in-israel/0000018e-94fe-d4de-afee-f4ff167b0000</guid></item><item><title>希伯伦山区巴勒斯坦人生活的镜头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-lens-on-the-life-of-palestinians-in-the-hebron-hills/0000018e-9947-d764-adff-9fcffc3c0000</link><description>诺加·卡林斯基 (Noga Kalinsky) 在 Masafer Yatta 地区拍摄的照片捕捉到了约旦河西岸希伯伦南部山区的自然之美和巴勒斯坦人民的苦难</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 11:21:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-lens-on-the-life-of-palestinians-in-the-hebron-hills/0000018e-9947-d764-adff-9fcffc3c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名作家萨米·迈克尔去世，享年 97 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/famed-israeli-author-sami-michael-dies-at-97/0000018e-991e-dd2b-ad9f-d95e4cbd0000</link><description>伊拉克出生的迈克尔是以色列最多产的作家之一，也被称为剧作家、翻译家、社会活动家和以色列民权协会主席。 2018 年，他对《国土报》表示，“文化的主要作用是照亮无知、不公正和腐败”</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 10:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/famed-israeli-author-sami-michael-dies-at-97/0000018e-991e-dd2b-ad9f-d95e4cbd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队从加沙的希法医院撤军，巴勒斯坦人报告行动后造成巨大破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-leaves-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-palestinians-report-vast-destruction/0000018e-98a5-d9a4-a7bf-dcfd04900000</link><description>以色列军队在完成为期两周的行动后离开了医院大楼，根据哈马斯救援部门的报告，该行动导致所有医院病房无法使用，并在现场留下约 300 具尸体</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 08:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-leaves-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-palestinians-report-vast-destruction/0000018e-98a5-d9a4-a7bf-dcfd04900000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的紧张失误揭示了他真正的首要任务：不惜一切代价维持自己的政治生存</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-nervous-slips-show-his-real-priority-his-own-political-survival-at-any-cost/0000018e-9881-da88-afff-fdbdfbfd0000</link><description>像任何受惊的独裁者一样，内塔尼亚胡采用了指责政治对手帮助敌人的熟悉策略。他的真实信息很明确：他的生存比人质或国家更重要</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 08:25:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-nervous-slips-show-his-real-priority-his-own-political-survival-at-any-cost/0000018e-9881-da88-afff-fdbdfbfd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的两名士兵的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/idf-releases-names-of-two-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018e-9860-d4de-afee-f86dfa6e0000</link><description>中士。一等兵韦尔于周五在汗尤尼斯附近受伤身亡，而参谋长。科恩周日在加沙地带南部被杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 07:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/idf-releases-names-of-two-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018e-9860-d4de-afee-f86dfa6e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军决定在以色列北部重新开放高中，但令家长们不相信</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-lets-galilee-high-schools-reopen-parents-are-unconvinced/0000018e-9612-d9a4-a7bf-de5b53930000</link><description>以色列军队鼓励以色列北部被疏散的地区重新开放两所高中，但学生往返学校行程的模糊性迫使家长陷入临时教育框架造成的困境</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-lets-galilee-high-schools-reopen-parents-are-unconvinced/0000018e-9612-d9a4-a7bf-de5b53930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对战后加沙的“多国部队”宣传只不过是一厢情愿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-multinational-force-pitch-for-postwar-gaza-is-little-more-than-wishful-thinking/0000018e-9614-dd2f-a7cf-d73d4a060000</link><description>随着战后加沙谈判变得更加紧迫，战后由哪个军事实体重建加沙地带的问题变得更加复杂——美国不愿意，巴勒斯坦权力机构不能，而任何愿意派遣军队的阿拉伯国家都将被指责与以色列勾结。职业</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-multinational-force-pitch-for-postwar-gaza-is-little-more-than-wishful-thinking/0000018e-9614-dd2f-a7cf-d73d4a060000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者在以色列与哈马斯人质谈判中向内塔尼亚胡施加压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/protesters-up-the-pressure-on-netanyahu-amid-israel-hamas-hostage-negotiations/0000018e-9620-da88-afff-f73d569e0000</link><description>当前的示威浪潮自战争开始以来首次对内塔尼亚胡构成挑战 ■ 哈马斯允许巴勒斯坦居民自由返回加沙北部的要求是以色列方面人质谈判的争论焦点</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/protesters-up-the-pressure-on-netanyahu-amid-israel-hamas-hostage-negotiations/0000018e-9620-da88-afff-f73d569e0000</guid></item><item><title>东耶路撒冷定居点获得数百万美元修建运动场 - 巴勒斯坦邻国却没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-settlement-gets-millions-for-sports-field-palestinian-neighbors-go-without/0000018e-95f1-d229-adae-95f302860000</link><description>东耶路撒冷的犹太飞地诺夫锡安 (Nof Zion) 的 90 个家庭将获得一个市政府资助的运动场，而周围的 Jebel Mukkaber 社区的 30,000 名居民却缺乏这个运动场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-settlement-gets-millions-for-sports-field-palestinian-neighbors-go-without/0000018e-95f1-d229-adae-95f302860000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列在大马士革袭击中杀死伊朗革命卫队高级将领</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-live/netanyahus-surgery-successful-three-wounded-in-southern-israel-stabbing-attack/0000018e-9762-d9a4-a7bf-df7bcabb0000</link><description>拜登和内塔尼亚胡助手实际上讨论了以色列入侵拉法的计划 ■ 以色列国防军称，在伊拉克亲伊朗民兵宣布袭击以色列的“关键目标”后，无人机于周一夜间在军事基地坠毁 ■ 以色列国防军称，来自 Al-Shifa 袭击的情报可能会产生有关人质的重要信息，巴勒斯坦人报告数百具尸体和广泛的破坏</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 02:58:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-live/netanyahus-surgery-successful-three-wounded-in-southern-israel-stabbing-attack/0000018e-9762-d9a4-a7bf-df7bcabb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列机构报告自 10 月 7 日以来网络攻击大幅增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-agency-reports-significant-surge-in-cyberattacks-since-oct-7/0000018e-95dc-d9a4-a7bf-dddd37b30000</link><description>以色列国家网络局的报告发现，去年报告的超过 13,000 起针对民用目标的网络攻击中，有 68% 发生在 10 月 7 日之后</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 00:42:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-agency-reports-significant-surge-in-cyberattacks-since-oct-7/0000018e-95dc-d9a4-a7bf-dddd37b30000</guid></item></channel></rss>